### 연속형 변수


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
weights_tbl <- penguins |> 
  drop_na() |> 
  group_by(species) |> 
  summarise(평균체중 = mean(body_mass_g),
            SD체중  = sd(body_mass_g),
            최소체중 = min(body_mass_g),
            최대체중 = max(body_mass_g))

weights <- weights_tbl |> 
  pull(평균체중)

weights
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```
[1] 3706.164 3733.088 5092.437
```
:::
